<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Thallian Fleetfoot</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-09 18:55:22</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Where do you get a sword like this?</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Chaotix</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-18 16:20:02</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I was lucky enough to win a /ran for this sword.  It dropped off of a Coerced Erudite (SK) in Dalnir (accessed through Warsilk Woods in Kunark).  Not sure if it is indicated above, but it is also a LORE ITEM.<BR>
<BR>
One thing to note:  The Coerced NPCs in Dalnir do not necessarily carry or even use the weapon that they rarely drop(at least up to this point in patching).  The erudite SK was punching with no obvious weapon and he still dropped the sword.<BR>
<BR>
Since I am on the subject of Dalnir, all Coerced NPCs are surprisingly summoned creatures.  Get a mage to summon you 2 rune swords and hack away while procing ward summoned.  Very nice.<BR>
<BR>
Chaotix Extreemus<BR>
(26th season warrior on Morrel-Thule)</font></td></tr></table>
