<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Cambron</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-23 05:21:29</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>     Myself and my brother Mikall (30th) were adventuring in Dalnir when we came upon the Coerced Erudite SK. She fought well but was no match for my Harpoon and my brother's spells. Although she was not swinging it, she did drop it. It is a good 2hs weapon for the short time I was using it. I will keep it in my inventory for future use. I would recomend it for the pure tanks.... good damage and good speed.<BR>
